<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Internship Application Status</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #222; }
      .container { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; }
      .title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
      .status { padding: 4px 8px; background: #f4f4f5; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block; }
      .footer { margin-top: 24px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="title">Your internship application status was updated</div>
      <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
      <p>Your application for the <strong><%= internshipField %></strong> internship is now: <span class="status"><%= status %></span>.</p>
      <% if (status === 'accepted') { %>
        <p>Congratulations! Our team will contact you with next steps shortly.</p>
      <% } else if (status === 'rejected') { %>
        <p>Thank you for your interest. Unfortunately we won't be moving forward at this time. We appreciate your effort and encourage you to apply again in the future.</p>
      <% } else { %>
        <p>We will keep you posted on further updates.</p>
      <% } %>
      <div class="footer">This is an automated message. Please do not reply.</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
